# The repo-root .gitignore excludes any directory literally named "bin/"
# (a .NET build-output convention used elsewhere in this monorepo), which
# would otherwise also swallow rust/src/bin/ — the idiomatic Cargo layout
# for the headscan-cases binary target (CONTRACT.md §1.3). Un-ignore it
# here, scoped to this fixture only.
!/rust/src/bin/
!/rust/src/bin/**

# Ephemeral checkout scratch space for tools/apply-delta.ps1
# (fixtures/slice-zero/workspace/checkouts/rust-<delta>/, regenerated on
# demand, never committed). Already covered by the repo-root .gitignore's
# "fixtures/slice-zero/workspace/" entry; restated here so this directory's
# intent is clear from inside fixtures/slice-zero/ alone.
/workspace/
